        <p>
            Choosing the right accommodation can really impact your vacation.
        </p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-default btn-primary" href="https://www.forbes.com/sites/christopherelliott/2019/05/11/a-new-trick-for-finding-the-best-vacation-rental/#4d6264084500">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-md-4">
        @*<i class="far fa-cocktail"></i>*@
        <h2>Relax</h2>
        <img class="img-rounded" src="~/Images/relax.png" alt="Alternate Text" />
        <p>
            It's always time to find a vacation to help you relax and forget about your work life.
        </p>
        <p><a class="btn btn-default btn-primary" href="http://mentalfloss.com/article/60627/11-hidden-benefits-taking-more-vacation">Learn more &raquo;</a></p>
    </div>
</div>

